      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MAXIMUM SUNSET (2) missed the frame latest when fifth at Ballarat (22.48) but scored four back at this track (23.36). Has never been out of the placings from two starts out of this box. Key runner on her best form. PAW PRYDI (1) missed the frame and was safely held latest finishing 8th at Ballarat following on from a second place finish (22.06) there the start prior. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings three times from five starts. Deserves plenty of respect. INITIAL CONSULT (4) jumped from box 8 last time and ran away with an impressive win scoring by 6 lengths at this track in a handy 23.44. Will need some luck early after drawing a tricky box here. Likely to be in the finish. PAW DANGER (6) cannot be left out after placing last start.",
